OL,3,CMiners' strike: Life on the picket
OL,4,Cline from the people who were there
OL,6,FRachel Bullock speaks to the people
OL,7,Fwho were on the front line during the
OL,8,Fminers' strike of 1984-5
OL,10,FIt was the strike that defined a
OL,11,Fdecade. The miners' strike. Its impact
OL,12,Flong lasting.
OL,14,FSome 23,000 of the North East's men
OL,15,Fwere on the picket line 40 years ago
OL,16,Fin what was the biggest industrial
OL,17,Faction the country has ever seen.
OL,19,FThey were fighting to save their pits,
OL,20,Ftheir jobs, their livelihoods.
