OL,3,CMiners' strike: Life on the picket
OL,4,Cline from the people who were there
OL,6,FOn the 99th day of strike action the
OL,7,Fscale of the fight was laid bare. The
OL,8,FBattle of Orgreave in Rotherham has
OL,9,Fgone down as one of the most violent
OL,10,Fclashes in history and involved
OL,11,Fpicketers and police.
OL,13,FMiners have long said police were used
OL,14,Fabove and beyond their duties to
OL,15,Fcontrol picketing and for Alan
OL,16,FMardghum, of Wearmouth Colliery,
OL,17,Factions of the authorities are
OL,18,F"unforgivable".
