OL,3,CMiners' strike: Life on the picket
OL,4,Cline from the people who were there
OL,6,FBut it was not long before other
OL,7,Fworkers would follow. The turn of
OL,8,Fwinter brought a new offer - a #650
OL,9,Fbonus for every miner who would return
OL,10,Fto work. Almost #3,000 today.
OL,12,FFor some it was enough, for others it
OL,13,Fwas just 30 pieces of silver.
OL,15,FMr Bell explained: "I spoke to them
OL,16,Fbefore they went back, I said to them
OL,17,F'I thought they were making a
OL,18,Fmistake'. I thought it was coming to
OL,19,Fan end anyway.
