OL,3,CMiners' strike: Life on the picket
OL,4,Cline from the people who were there
OL,6,FMr Bell said: "I would have stayed on
OL,7,Fstrike forever.
OL,9,F"Since I finished coal mining, I've
OL,10,Fgot a degree, I built a business. I
OL,11,Fidentify as being a coal miner. I'm
OL,12,Fvery very proud of it. It's who I am."
